platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Make a routine & put on a show
Monte sur scne avec ta chor

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Bursting with beats and energy, Toca Dance will make the whole family want to get up and groove. This incredibly cute game puts kids in charge of their own musical productionchoosing dancers, costumes, and techno tracks, and choreographing moves using simple swipes and taps. Once the performance starts, the real fun begins: you can fling items at the stage, set off pyrotechnics and other cool effects, and even cheer (or boo) your squad. Seeing the payoffan awesome video you can sharewill encourage players to jump right back in and start working on their next great show.
